_sText: ------------------------------ Surf_buck-around (#4 in the BUCK series) Map created by Buck Nasty Skybox by Hipshot Skateboard props by Sherow_Xx ------------------------------ This is pretty much the sequel to surf_buck-wild - Combat/kill type surf map - Bombsite is disable for the first minute - Buyzone is located above jail - The bullseye pads shoot you up in the air - Jail opens every 30 seconds for ~18 seconds - The secret room/hall has been updated and extended with some new secrets - Guns: AK-47, AUG, G3SG1, M3, M4A1, MP5NAVY, P-90, SCOUT, SG552, UMP45 - I ran some alphas and betas, so there shouldn't be any bugs in the map. - Thanks to all those who helped me test this map! - Comments/compliments are always welcome, including constructive criticism (but i won't use the constructive crit. cause this map is final) - My Server IP css.nyfiber.net:30000 - Join my steam group http://steamcommunity.com/groups/bucknastysurf - http://waspnest.net/ - http://solidsurf.info/ Enjoy! --Buck Nasty
